<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 00:58:16 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>科威尔在亚冠夺冠后保持警惕</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/kewell-guards-against-complacency-after-asian-champions-league-win-2024-05-11/</link><description>尽管在周六的亚洲冠军联赛决赛中，他率领横滨水手队在主场以 2-1 领先，但主教练哈里·科威尔仍然对埃尔南·克雷斯波的艾因队构成的威胁保持警惕。</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 22:09:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/kewell-guards-against-complacency-after-asian-champions-league-win-2024-05-11/</guid></item><item><title>另有八个中国城市加入香港独自旅游计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/eight-more-chinese-cities-join-hong-kong-solo-travel-scheme-2024-05-11/</link><description>又有八个中国城市加入了一项计划，允许居民自行前往香港，而不是跟团，作为促进香港经济的努力的一部分。</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 13:22:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/eight-more-chinese-cities-join-hong-kong-solo-travel-scheme-2024-05-11/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾派遣船只前往中国建造“人工岛”的争议环礁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-sends-ships-disputed-atoll-where-china-building-artificial-island-2024-05-11/</link><description>菲律宾周六表示，已向南海争议地区部署船只，并指责中国在不断升级的海上争端中建造“人工岛”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 11:03:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-sends-ships-disputed-atoll-where-china-building-artificial-island-2024-05-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国碧桂园在宽限期内偿还境内优惠券</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-country-garden-repays-onshore-coupons-within-grace-period-2024-05-11/</link><description>陷入困境的中国房地产开发商碧桂园在周六的一份声明中表示，继上周未能付款后，该公司已在五天宽限期到期前偿还了两笔境内债券票息。</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 09:46:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-country-garden-repays-onshore-coupons-within-grace-period-2024-05-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国公司赢得伊拉克油气田勘探许可</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/iraq-launches-oil-gas-licensing-round-29-projects-2024-05-11/</link><description>周六，中国公司在一轮碳氢化合物勘探许可中赢得了勘探伊拉克五个油气田的投标，该轮勘探主要旨在提高国内天然气产量。</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 08:17:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/iraq-launches-oil-gas-licensing-round-29-projects-2024-05-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国居民消费价格连续第三个月上涨 预示需求复苏</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-consumer-prices-rise-3rd-month-factory-deflation-persists-2024-05-11/</link><description>4月份，中国消费者价格连续第三个月上涨，而生产者价格则延续跌势，这表明在北京应对提振经济的挑战之际，内需有所改善。</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 01:48:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-consumer-prices-rise-3rd-month-factory-deflation-persists-2024-05-11/</guid></item><item><title>美国在气候谈判中讨论了中国太阳能制造和煤炭的“产能过剩”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/us-discussed-overcapacity-chinese-solar-manufacturing-coal-climate-talks-2024-05-10/</link><description>美国国务院高级官员周五表示，美国和中国在为期两天的气候变化双边会议上讨论了中国太阳能和电池制造、钢铁生产和煤炭发电的产能过剩问题。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 18:24:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/us-discussed-overcapacity-chinese-solar-manufacturing-coal-climate-talks-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行承诺支持经济复苏</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-central-bank-pledges-support-economic-recovery-2024-05-10/</link><description>中国央行周五表示，将确保流动性合理充裕和信贷扩张，巩固经济复苏，但经济复苏仍面临诸多挑战。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 17:17:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-central-bank-pledges-support-economic-recovery-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，在美国上市面临障碍的情况下，Shein 加强了伦敦 IPO 的准备工作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/shein-steps-up-london-ipo-preparations-amid-us-hurdles-listing-sources-say-2024-05-10/</link><description>两位知情人士表示，快时尚巨头 Shein 正在加紧准备在伦敦上市，此前该公司试图在纽约上市，但面临监管障碍和美国立法者的阻力。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 16:01:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/shein-steps-up-london-ipo-preparations-amid-us-hurdles-listing-sources-say-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车制造商 Zeekr 在美国市场首次亮相，股价飙升近 35%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-zeekr-set-debut-nyse-after-upsized-ipo-2024-05-10/</link><description>周五，Zeekr 的股价较首次公开募股价格上涨近 35%，这为这家电动汽车制造商带来了强劲的开局，这是自 2021 年以来首家中国公司在美国主要市场首次亮相。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 10:48:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-zeekr-set-debut-nyse-after-upsized-ipo-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>4月份中国汽车出口创历史新高，但国内销量下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-april-car-sales-swing-contraction-despite-nev-milestone-2024-05-10/</link><description>周五的数据显示，由于价格竞争加剧以及消费者在经济复苏不稳定的情况下对大件消费持谨慎态度，国内销量同比下滑 5.8%，中国 4 月份汽车出口飙升至历史新高。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 08:45:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-april-car-sales-swing-contraction-despite-nev-milestone-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国表示坚决反对美国出口管制工具</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-says-it-firmly-opposes-us-export-control-tools-2024-05-10/</link><description>在美国出于国家安全考虑将37家中国企业列入贸易限制名单后，外交部发言人周五表示，中国坚决反对滥用美国实体清单等出口管制工具。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 08:24:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-says-it-firmly-opposes-us-export-control-tools-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>Porch 在美国起诉中国建设银行再保险欺诈损失</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/porch-sues-china-construction-bank-us-over-reinsurance-fraud-losses-2024-05-10/</link><description>美国保险和房屋检查软件提供商 Porch 集团正在起诉中国资产第三大银行中国建设银行 (CCB)，指控其实施“大规模欺诈”，给 Porch 造成“巨大损失”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 08:20:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/porch-sues-china-construction-bank-us-over-reinsurance-fraud-losses-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国军方称其在南海“击退”了美国驱逐舰</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-military-says-it-drove-away-us-destroyer-south-china-sea-2024-05-10/</link><description>解放军南部战区周五在一份声明中表示，中国军队严密监视并“驱离”了5月10日进入南海西沙群岛领海的哈尔西号驱逐舰。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 07:29:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-military-says-it-drove-away-us-destroyer-south-china-sea-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>富士康第一季度利润从低基数跃升，人工智能推动增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/foxconns-q1-profit-jump-low-base-ai-power-growth-2024-05-10/</link><description>全球最大的合同电子产品制造商台湾富士康预计将于周二报告称，由于人工智能服务器的强劲需求以及去年同期的低基数，第一季度利润将增长一倍以上。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 06:44:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/foxconns-q1-profit-jump-low-base-ai-power-growth-2024-05-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>